The Woodsman;;77;;88;;R;;After 12 years in prison, Walter (Kevin Bacon) returns home. Few people know he's a sex offender and pedophile. Walter finds an apartment where he's regularly visited by his parole officer (Mos Def). He gets a job at a lumber mill and starts seeing a coworker (Kyra Sedgwick). Then his new world begins to unravel. As his past becomes known, he begins a high-risk friendship with a young girl and realizes that a man loitering near a schoolyard is a child molester prowling for his next victim.;;Drama;;Nicole Kassell;;2004;;Kevin Bacon,Kyra Sedgwick,Eve,Yasiin Bey,David Alan Grier,Benjamin Bratt,Michael Shannon,Hannah Pilkes,Carlos Leon,Gina Philips;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/woodsman